						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">King: Kulōttuṅga (I) Year 25: 1095-96 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Slightly damaged. Records that the <hi rend="italic">mahāsabhai</hi> of Śivakūḍal sold a piece of land, one <hi rend="italic">vēli</hi>, after the receipt of price-money from Ādichaṇḍēśvara of the temple for providing food offerings to the god Mahādēvar Śivakoḻundāṇḍār of the village.</p>						

