<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> tribhu</hi>vanacca<unclear>k</unclear>karava<hi rend="grantha">tdhi</hi>kaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> kulottuṅ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ka coḻa<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>vaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="25">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 5</num> civakūṭal <hi rend="grantha">mahāsabhai</hi>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>yom Eṅkaḷ ma<hi rend="grantha">hāde</hi>var civakkoḻun=taṇṭārku ma<hi rend="grantha">ntra</hi>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ponakam Amuti ceykaiy<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied>ku I<hi rend="grantha">de</hi>var Ā<hi rend="grantha">didā</hi>
<lb n="5" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>n<hi rend="grantha">caṇḍeśvara de</hi>var pakkal vilai koṇ
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṭu viṟṟukkuṭutta nilamāvatu Emmur kamalanā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>rāyaṇapputteri Etirvāy vaṭakuṟukku pā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>yaneri kiḻ kiḻ<unclear>pā</unclear>ṟkellai(kaḷa) ten
<lb n="9"/>vaṭakku meṟkum tenpāṟkellai ca <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/>n kāviri ninṟum meṟku nokkippa<unclear>p</unclear>oṉa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="11"/>kuṟṟa karaikkuvaṭakkum melpāṟkel<unclear>laimāka</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="12"/>marutaiy maṅkalattellaikku kiḻakku
<lb n="13"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="14"/>kku teṟkum Inṉānkellaikkuḷ naṭuvu
<lb n="15"/>paṭṭa nilam Uṇṇilamoḻiviṉṟi Emmi
<lb n="16" break="no"/>licai<supplied reason="omitted">nta</supplied> vilaipporuḷ muṟṟum Āvaṇakka
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ḷiye <supplied reason="omitted">vi</supplied>ṟṟuvilaikkāṇaṅ kiḻikaic cela
<lb n="18" break="no"/>pe <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> koṇṭu vilaiyaṟṟu viṟṟu An
</p>

<p>This inscription stops here. Just below this another inscription, written slightly differently, which seems to be connected with this, runs as follows:</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/>koḻutāṇṭār Ā<hi rend="grantha">didāsa</hi>n<hi rend="grantha">caṇḍeśvarade</hi>varpa <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/><unclear>k</unclear>oṇṭu nāṅkaḷ viṟṟukkuṭutta nilamāvatu kiḻkaḻa<unclear>ni</unclear> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>ṭṭup paṟaiccerik kiḻitu turan=tarapperuñceṟu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>Itiṉ meṟkil koyilāṉkuḻiyiṉ teṟ <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>Oru veliyum viṟṟuk kuṭuppataṟku kiḻpāṟke
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> lān kuḻimaṭai pān=ta vāykkālukku meṟkum teṉ pā
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

